            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "coming"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Bm",
              "text": "into"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "He's not"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "just a teaching,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or a"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "creed or"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "a dead"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Em",
              "text": "doctrine,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "processed"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Triune"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "God, glori"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "ous!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is not created"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As man’s body, soul, and spirit—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That’s man’s life that’s weak and temporal."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is uncreated."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s divine and it’s eternal."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And this is the life that’s indestructible."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And this life came in us"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our spirit through the Spirit;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is where we were made alive!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now this life is spreading."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, don’t stop—just keep invading."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For this, Lord, we must be daily revived."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life needs our maintaining,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Otherwise we’re suffocating."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Calling on His name we breathe Him in."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Everywhere we breathe Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Makes us fresh and makes us living."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O, this life is full of hope and meaning."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our daily living"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s this life that we are sensing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are we in the flesh or in the Lord?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you’re dead and empty"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And the troubles you have plenty,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Saints, get out of there and flee back to the Lord!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then you’ll sense life flowing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s this life that’s overcoming"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Satan, flesh, and the world, and sin."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What a life we’re having."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, Your virtues manifesting,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, we’re branches bearing fruit in John 15."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
  ],
